:

*Pokušavaš* da poboljšaš svoje veštine. (You're trying to improve your skills.)
*Pokušavala* sam da naučim nove stvari. (I was trying to learn new things.)
*Pokušavao* je da postane novi vođa. (He was trying to become the new leader.)
*Pokušavam* da promenim način razmišljanja. (I'm trying to change the way I think.)
*Pokušavamo* da pronađemo rešenje. (We're trying to find a solution.)